sentences: Bridget Kelly (born April 8, 1986) is an American singer and songwriter from New York City.

In 2008, Kelly, a pop and R&B recording artist, who has written songs for fellow American singers such as Kelly Clarkson, secured a recording contract with American rapper and hip-hop mogul Jay-Z's record label Roc Nation.
